<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7831> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7831" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "On the date in 205, not 209, for his aedileship, see above, on L. Cornelius Lentulus (188), Cos. 199.\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7831 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2608> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2608" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "A. Postumius Albinus (Luscus) succeeded L. Cornelius Lentulus. Liv. 42.10.6. On Lentulus, see 213, note 8; on Postumius, Münzer, Bull. Com., 67 (1939) 27-30; Lübker, no. 3." ;
	dprr:hasID 2608 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1649> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1649" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Liv. 27.21.9; 29.11.12" ;
	dprr:hasID 1649 .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/1647> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #1647" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "On the identity of this Aedile, see Münzer RE. The praenomen L. has been omitted in II, and is supplied by the corrector A\n   \n    7\n   \n   , whose readings Conway and Johnson have found generally reliable (see app. crit. to 26.51.8, and preface § 97). The name of Q. Caecilius Metellus rests upon the same tradition. See Conway and Johnson ad loc." ;
	dprr:hasID 1647 .
